metadata.name: MIDDLE OF VIETNAM B&W
metadata.description:
The geographic heart of the nation, central Vietnam is packed with historic sights and cultural interest. The people here is super friendly and work hard.
This image was captured at Binh Thuan Province was part of the Cham principality of Panduranga It was the last independent principality after the fall of Vijaya in 1471.
Captured using Canon 6d + 70-200 IS f2.8, 2014.
